" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T19:47:12.000Z","msg":"都算，講咖喱都可以屌晒老母開戰咁款呢個就真係犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T19:50:41.000Z","msg":"十個連登POST 九個入到去D人都係互屌緊老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T19:54:23.000Z","msg":"食咖哩都比人屌，遲d呼吸都比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9e7aed70605810ab735aef17693dc9620d081c","tid":781264,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"個人感覺東南亞咖哩真係一種好特別嘅菜式即使唔同地方有唔同分別<br />\n但日本咖哩就好似除左個名外好唔同，似一種汁多過會想分類佢係咖哩入面<br />\n<br />\n不過我兩種都鍾意（東南亞個邊嘅更鐘意多啲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134c28f8e7f55830317d1d3a2515a68528e85102","tid":781264,"uid":178800,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T20:22:11.000Z","msg":"支持樓主,<br />\n每次想食咖哩都會忍住第二日加拿大會有陣味既情況下<br />\n專登搵印度/東南亞咖哩<br />\n絕對唔係食日式咖哩<br />\n難聽D比喻,日或咖哩就係SPICY既葡汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5a6bc8806a033df5aff2ae750358a4cec68fc1","tid":781264,"uid":77054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T20:23:50.000Z","msg":"企鵝係咪鵝"},{"pid":"477f049ba88f8c793945c5d4d1b1078e35a3ade6","tid":781264,"uid":18977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T20:26:08.000Z","msg":"走啦印度佬 食咁重味因著痾咖哩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申唔食咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b757c43d09f9943a0d74c0016e985fc493b367","tid":781264,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08