cddcf","tid":781264,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:16:30.000Z","msg":"兩種都好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都可以攞黎嘈一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfe07f97e1e260e92f896761f14fd738fbbe916","tid":781264,"uid":10890,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:26:18.000Z","msg":"咖哩本身係一種醬<br />\n冇統一食譜<br />\n每家每戶都可以有自己嘅食譜有自己嘅做法<br />\n你可以話一樣咖哩唔好食<br />\n但唔可以話佢侮辱咗咖哩呢個名<br />\n因為咖哩係冇限定用咩香料同點整<br />\n<br />\n當泰式青咖哩可以用香茅、椰漿、魚露嚟整嘅時候<br />\n而馬拉咖哩又會用椰漿、椰絲、芭蕉葉<br />\n點解日本人唔可以加啲果蓉嚟整個日式咖哩？"},{"pid":"52e4d7ee5d6ca8656dd7a35e47408eccb9fafcbf","tid":781264,"uid":46151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:31:48.000Z","msg":"其實咖喱呢個字 本身佢嘅意思就只不過係解醬<br />\n醬有唔同口味有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514d413b062f402b9994693ee1503421d5440bd8","tid":781264,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:32:55.000Z","msg":"以為會有日式咖喱蝸牛，我都係出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097e8223771b25746e0712b964b01bad794bd70e","tid":781264,"uid":143471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:35:39.000Z","msg":"屌好撚肚餓"},{"pid":"54fc0c870a0c6e87e51bff66e4f52dd5738281f6","tid":781264,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:42:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14b6d5872660e7be0db561bddc5e5c16949db4b","tid":781264,"uid":38725,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:47:45.000Z","msg":"樓主D論點弱智到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78e4921452504ddb97ba4a5c505541ade710108","tid":781264,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:51:24.000Z","msg":"都係薑黃大小茴香做底<br />\n係用左大量野菜做左個甜味出黎姐"},{"pid":"5ab09dc5f05509d71229013a1d649e1fb4bef331","